thread.title: BRIEF-Southwest Airlines Reports March Load Factor 85.1 Pct Vs 84.1 Pct Year Ago

title: BRIEF-Southwest Airlines Reports March Load Factor 85.1 Pct Vs 84.1 Pct Year Ago
text:
April 6, 2018 / 10:40 AM / Updated 3 minutes ago BRIEF-Southwest Airlines Reports March Load Factor 85.1 Pct Vs 84.1 Pct Year Ago Reuters Staff 
April 6 (Reuters) - Southwest Airlines Co: * SOUTHWEST AIRLINES REPORTS MARCH TRAFFIC 
* SOUTHWEST AIRLINES CO MARCH LOAD FACTOR 85.1 PCT VS 84.1 PCT YR AGO 
* SOUTHWEST AIRLINES CO - FLEW 11.7 BLN REV PASSENGER MILES (RPMS) IN MARCH 2018, UP 3.7 PERCENT FROM 11.3 BLN RPMS FLOWN IN MARCH 2017 
* SOUTHWEST AIRLINES CO - AVAILABLE SEAT MILES (ASMS) INCREASED 2.4 PERCENT TO 13.8 BLN IN MARCH 2018 Source text for Eikon: Further company coverage:
